title: VOLLEYBALL: Laingsburg captures crown at Ovid-Elsie Invitational
text:
Argus-Press Photo/Chris Hauler Maya Ferland 
MAYA FERLAND (9) OF LAINGSBURG, right, powers a kill during the first game against Stanton Central Montcalm Saturday. The Wolfpack captured title honors at the Ovid-Elsie Invitational. Posted: Sunday, October 11, 2015 2:00 am VOLLEYBALL: Laingsburg captures crown at Ovid-Elsie Invitational By CHRIS HAULER, Argus-Press Sports Writer The Argus-Press | 0 comments 
ELSIE — Laingsburg coach Tennille Whitmore called it a total team effort as the Wolfpack scorched through the Ovid-Elsie Volleyball Invitational on Saturday. 
The Wolfpack didn’t lose a set and defeated Bath 25-18, 25-16 in the championship game to win the tourney. kAm“%96J 42>6 :?
